## Scope clarification

This MIT License covers the SOFTWARE in this repository (the ZUREON HUB
Next.js application): TON Connect 2.0 integration, wallet UI/UX flows, AI
Review request-building logic, STON.fi swap payload construction, and all
supporting TypeScript/React application code and build tooling under `src/`.

The AI proxy backend, rate limiting, and prompt-injection guard this app
calls (`/.netlify/functions/ai-proxy`) live in ZUREON's main site repository
and are not part of this repository.

